A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend Part 2 of Article 15 of Chapter 1 of Title 10 and Article 13 of Chapter 1 of Title 7
2 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to the Fair Business Practices Act and
3 licensing of mortgage lenders and mortgage brokers, respectively, so as to prohibit unfair or
4 deceptive practices in consumer transactions related to mortgage trigger leads; to provide for
5 definitions; to provide for a remedy; to provide for related matters; to provide for an effective
6 date; to repeal conflicting laws; and for other purposes.
7 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
8 SECTION 1.
9 Part 2 of Article 15 of Chapter 1 of Title 10 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated,
10 relating to the Fair Business Practices Act, is amended by adding a new Code section to read
11 as follows:
12 "10-1-393.20.
13 (a) As used in this Code section, the term:
14 (1) 'Mortgage broker' shall have the same meaning as set forth in Code Section 7-1-1000.
15 (2) 'Mortgage lender' shall have the same meaning as set forth in Code Section 7-1-1000.
